      "updated": 1771249854167,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "JVM are platform dependent\nevery platform have different\nJVM. we cant use Same JVM\nin Every platform.but BYTECODE \nare platform independent.\n\nso we dont have a single friend\nto tanslate every country lang\nwe have one friend in every\nplatform ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "JVM are platform dependent\nevery platform have different\nJVM. we cant use Same JVM\nin Every platform.but BYTECODE \nare platform independent.\n\nso we dont have a single friend\nto tanslate every country lang\nwe have one friend in every\nplatform ",
